Privacy Policy
Last Updated: February 2025

1. Introduction
Welcome to TeamManager! Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our app.

2. Information We Collect
We may collect the following types of data:

Personal Information: Name, email, and profile details.
Usage Data: Events you join, files downloaded, and communication logs.
Device Information: App usage statistics and device details.
3. How We Use Your Information
We use the collected data to:

Manage users, groups, and events.
Improve app performance and user experience.
Provide customer support and app updates.
Send important notifications regarding events or group activities.
4. Data Sharing & Security
We do not sell or share your personal data with third parties.
Your data is stored securely, but we cannot guarantee 100% security.
Only authorized users can access group-related information.
5. Your Rights
You have the right to:

Update or delete your account information.
Request access to the data we have about you.
Opt out of certain data collection features (where applicable).
6. Third-Party Services
Our app may include links to third-party services like Google Meet. We are not responsible for their privacy policies. Please review their terms before using them.

7. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any significant changes within the app or via email.

8. Contact Us
